-meta-take-care-dad-2025-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20India%20May%20Not%20Agree%20To%20'Zero-For-Zero%20Tariffs'%20With%20US%20Under%20Trade%20Deal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWith%20India%20and%20the%20United%20States%20set%20to%20begin%20virtual%20talks%20over%20the%20proposed%20bilateral%20trade%20agreement%20(BTA)%20this%20week%2C%20New%20Delhi%20is%20unlikely%20to%20agree%20to%20a%20zero-for-zero'%20tariff%20strategy%20with%20Washington.%20The%20two%20sides%20may%20also%20not%20go%20for%20item-by-item%20parity%20during%20these%20sector-specific%20talks%2C%20with%20negotiations%20revolving%20around%20bringing%20the%20overall%20tariff%20down%20from%20both%20sides%20amid%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20%26quot%3BAmerica%20first%26quot%3B%20policy%20push.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENew%20Delhi%20and%20Washington%20are%20scheduled%20to%20engage%20in%20sector-specific%20talks%20in%20the%20coming%20weeks%2C%20and%20the%20first%20phase%20of%20the%20trade%20deal%20between%20the%20US%20and%20India%20could%20be%20out%20within%20the%20tariff-pause%20period%20of%2090%20days.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20terms%20of%20reference%20for%20the%20pact%20have%20been%20finalised%2C%20and%20further%20negotiations%20are%20set%20to%20take%20place%20primarily%20over%20video%20conferencing%2C%20though%20negotiators%20may%20meet%20in%20person%20as%20well%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20by%20NDTV%20Profit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Will%20Be%20The%20Focus%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDiscussions%20around%20a%20broad%20package%20deal%20on%20tariffs%20and%20non-tariff%20barriers%20are%20likely%20to%20take%20precedence%20over%20achieving%20tariff%20parity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20and%20the%20U.S.%20may%20not%20go%20for%20item-by-item%20parity%20during%20these%20sector-specific%20talks%2C%20and%20the%20talks%20may%20revolve%20around%20shaping%20the%20deal%20on%20bringing%20the%20overall%20tariff%20down%20from%20both%20sides%2C%26quot%3B%20people%20in%20the%20know%20told%20NDTV%20Profit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Zero-For-Zero'%20Tariffs%20Unlikely%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20deal%20is%20also%20unlikely%20to%20have%20a%20zero-for-zero%20tariff%20strategy%20as%20the%20two%20countries%20are%20at%20different%20levels%20of%20economic%20development%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20by%20Press%20Trust%20Of%20India%20(PTI).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECertain%20trade%20experts%20have%20suggested%20that%20India%20can%20propose%20a%20'zero-for-zero'%20tariff%20strategy%20to%20the%20US%20for%20addressing%20President%20Trump's%20reciprocal%20tariff%20hikes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20an%20official%20told%20PTI%20that%20zero-for-zero%20tariffs%20can%20be%20possible%20between%20the%20US%20and%20the%20European%20Union%20(EU)%20as%20both%20are%20developed%20and%20advanced%20nations%2C%20but%20it%20would%20not%20pan%20out%20well%20between%20India%20and%20the%20US.%20Given%20India's%20relatively%20low%20per%20capita%20income%2C%20it%20would%20still%20need%20to%20keep%20reasonable%20tariffs%20for%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20goods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20zero-for-zero%20tariff%20approach%20is%20one%20where%20two%20nations%20identify%20specific%20product%20categories%20and%20eliminate%20the%20levies%20on%20them%2C%20instead%20of%20imposing%20a%20blanket%20range%20of%20tariffs%20or%20inking%20a%20broader%20trade%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20India-US%20agreement%20will%20always%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bpackage%26quot%3B%20deal%20that%20could%20include%20issues%20such%20as%20goods%20and%20non-tariff%20barriers%2C%20the%20official%20said%20adding%20%26quot%3Bit%20does%20not%20happen%20like%20this%20that%20if%20he%20will%20do%20'zero'%20in%20electronics%2C%20we%20will%20also%20do%20in%20electronics.%20Trade%20agreements%20do%20not%20happen%20like%20this.%20It%20is%20a%20wrong%20thinking%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20February%2C%20Delhi-based%20think%20tank%20GTRI%20suggested%20that%20India%20should%20propose%20a%20zero-for-zero%20tariff%20strategy%20to%20the%20US%20for%20addressing%20America's%20tariff%20hikes.%20Under%20this%20strategy%2C%20it%20was%20stated%20that%20India%20can%20identify%20tariff%20lines%20(or%20product%20categories)%20where%20it%20can%20eliminate%20import%20duties%20for%20American%20imports%20and%20in%20lieu%20of%20that%2C%20the%20US%20should%20also%20remove%20duties%20on%20a%20similar%20number%20of%20goods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20US%20is%20looking%20at%20duty%20concessions%20in%20sectors%20like%20certain%20industrial%20goods%2C%20automobiles%20(electric%20vehicles%20particularly)%2C%20wines%2C%20petrochemical%20products%2C%20dairy%2C%20agriculture%20items%20such%20as%20apples%2C%20tree%20nuts%2C%20and%20alfalfa%20hay%3B%20India%20may%20look%20at%20duty%20cuts%20for%20labour-intensive%20sectors%20like%20apparels%2C%20textiles%2C%20gems%20and%20jewellery%2C%20leather%2C%20plastics%2C%20chemicals%2C%20oil%20seeds%2C%20shrimp%2C%20and%20horticulture%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia-US%20BTA%20Talks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20and%20the%20US%20have%20been%20engaged%20in%20negotiating%20a%20bilateral%20trade%20agreement%20(BTA)%20since%20March.%20Both%20sides%20have%20targeted%20to%20conclude%20the%20first%20phase%20of%20the%20pact%20by%20the%20fall%20(September-October)%20of%20this%20year%2C%20with%20an%20aim%20to%20more%20than%20double%20the%20bilateral%20trade%20to%20USD%20500%20billion%20by%202030%20from%20about%20USD%20191%20billion%20currently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20work%20has%20started%20for%20the%20agreement.%20India%20is%20far%20ahead%20of%20other%20countries%20in%20negotiating%20a%20trade%20deal%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20official%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%202021-22%20to%202023-24%2C%20the%20US%20was%20India's%20largest%20trading%20partner.%20%C2%A0It%20accounts%20for%20about%2018%20per%20cent%20of%20India's%20total%20goods%20exports%2C%206.22%20per%20cent%20in%20imports%2C%20and%2010.73%20per%20cent%20in%20bilateral%20trade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20America%2C%20India%20had%20a%20trade%20surplus%20(the%20difference%20between%20imports%20and%20exports)%20of%20USD%2035.32%20billion%20in%20goods%20in%202023-24.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744623240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2F7jivra5g_modi-trump-reuters_625x300_14_February_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhy-india-may-not-agree-to-zero-for-zero-tariffs-with-us-under-trade-deal-8161078%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20India%20and%20the%20United%20States%20set%20to%20begin%20virtual%20talks%20over%20the%20proposed%20bilateral%20trade%20agreement%20(BTA)%20this%20week%2C%20New%20Delhi%20is%20unlikely%20to%20agree%20to%20a%20zero-for-zero'%20tariff%20strategy%20with%20Washington.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Fire%20Erupts%20At%20Hotel%20Where%20Sunrisers%20Hyderabad%20IPL%20Players%20Are%20Staying%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFire%20erupted%20this%20morning%20at%20a%20luxury%20hotel%20in%20Hyderabad%20where%20the%20players%20of%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%20home%20team%20are%20staying.%20The%20fire%20broke%20out%20on%20the%20first%20floor%20of%20Park%20Hyatt%20in%20the%20posh%20Banjara%20Hills%20locality%2C%20sending%20thick%20smoke%20across%20the%20corridors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirefighters%20soon%20reached%20the%20spot%20and%20brought%20it%20under%20control.%C2%A0The%20cause%20of%20the%20fire%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20ascertained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPlayers%20of%20the%20Sunrisers%20Hyderabad%20(SRH)%2C%20the%20local%20IPL%20franchise%2C%20are%20put%20up%20at%20the%20hotel.%C2%A0The%20pre-release%20function%20for%20the%20upcoming%20Telugu%20movie%20'Odela%202'%20was%20scheduled%20to%20be%2