Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%20Dr%20Ambedkar%20-%20once%20dismissed%20by%20mainstream%20politicians%20as%20a%20'sectarian%20figurehead'%20-%20and%20his%20legacy%20have%20been%20frequently%20called%20upon%20by%20political%20leaders%20to%20win%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20nothing%20has%20changed%20since%2C%20with%20the%20primary%20political%20actors%20-%20the%20BJP%20and%20Congress%20among%20them%20-%20lining%20up%20public%20meetings%20and%20programmes%20to%20garland%20statues%20over%20the%20next%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20so%20battlelines%20were%20drawn%20again%20Monday%2C%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20his%20BJP%20tossing%20jeers%20and%20alliterative%20barbs%20-%20'%3Cem%3Evote%20bank%20ka%20virus%3C%2Fem%3E'%20and%20'destroyer%20of%20Constitutions'%20this%20year%20-%20at%20the%20Congress%20and%20other%20opposition%20parties%2C%20including%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20and%20BSP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20Dr%20Ambedkar's%20rich%20legacy%20has%20come%20down%2C%20in%20large%20measure%2C%20to%20such%20squabbles%2C%20leaving%20the%20marginalised%20communities%20he%20fought%20for%20as%20the%20'prize'%2C%20is%20a%20sad%20statement%20in%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESadder%20still%20is%20a%20situation%20many%20believe%20sidesteps%20his%20warnings%20on%20religious%20fundamentalism%20and%20upper%20caste%20dominance%2C%20and%20insistence%20on%20safeguards%20in%20the%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EPM%20vs%20Congress%20On%20Ambedkar%20Jayanti%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202025%20squabble%20over%20Dr%20Ambedkar's%20legacy%20began%20this%20morning%20with%20Mr%20Modi%20attacking%20the%20Congress%20for%20opposing%20amendments%20to%20the%20Waqf%20Act%2C%20and%20accusing%20it%20of%20having%20sabotaged%20Dr%20Ambedkar's%20electoral%20fortunes%20in%20the%201952%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20and%20the%201954%20Bhandara%20bypoll.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20must%20never%20forget%20what%20the%20Congress%20did%20to%20Babasaheb%20Ambedkar.%20While%20he%20was%20alive%2C%20the%20party%20insulted%20him...%20made%20him%20lose%20elections%20twice.%20Congress%20wanted%20to%20uproot%20him...%20they%20conspired%20to%20keep%20him%20out%20of%20the%20system%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20raged%20in%20Haryana's%20Hisar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress'%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20hit%20back%20by%20red-flagging%20delayed%20reservation%20of%20a%20third%20of%20parliamentary%20and%20Assembly%20seats%20for%20women%2C%20as%20'proof'%20the%20BJP%20does%20not%20actually%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20has%20also%20re-flagged%20last%20year's%20row%20over%20Amit%20Shah's%20Rajya%20Sabha%20comments%3B%20the%20Home%20Minister%20had%20said%20taking%20Dr%20Ambedkar's%20name%20had%20become%20the%20%26quot%3Bfashion%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20had%20responded%20fiercely%20then%2C%20claiming%20the%20remark%20proved%20the%20BJP%20and%20its%20ideological%20parent%2C%20the%20RSS%2C%20%26quot%3Bwanted%20to%20implement%20%3Cem%3EManusmriti%20%3C%2Fem%3Einstead%20of%20the%20Constitution%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EAkhilesh%20Yadav%2C%20Rest%20Chip%20In%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20AAP%2C%20defeated%20in%20Delhi%20by%20the%20BJP%2C%20has%20waded%20in%20too%2C%20with%20party%20boss%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20accusing%20both%20the%20BJP%20and%20Congress%20of%20having%20neglected%20Dr%20Ambedkar's%20legacy.%20Only%20his%20party%20had%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20claimed%2C%20pointing%20to%20the%20focus%20on%20education%20when%20it%20ruled%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20we%20did%20not%20allow%20private%20schools%20(in%20Delhi)%20to%20increase%20fees%20but%2C%20as%20soon%20as%20the%20BJP%20government%20came%2C%20private%20schools%20pounced%20upon%20them%20(the%20parents)%20like%20wolves...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20the%20AAP%20and%20BJP%20also%20went%20head-to-head%20over%20repositioning%20portraits%20of%20Dr%20Ambedkar%20in%20the%20office%20of%20the%20new%20Chief%20Minister%20-%20Rekha%20Gupta.%20These%20were%20moved%20to%20the%20side%20walls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESamajwadi%20Party%20boss%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20and%20BSP%20chief%20Mayawati%20also%20made%20declarations%20on%20expected%20lines%2C%20hailing%20the%20Constitution%20that%20Dr%20Ambedkar%20drafted%20and%20demanding%20the%20emancipation%20of%20marginalised%20communities%2C%20including%20Dalits%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20back-and-forth%20isn't%20just%20about%20rhetoric%20or%20one-upmanship.%20It%20is%2C%20as%20it%20always%20is%20in%20politics%2C%20about%20scoring%20brownie%20points%20with%20voters%2C%20particularly%20with%20an%20election%20due%20in%20Bihar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20about%20the%20Constitution%20and%20the%20amended%20Waqf%20Act%20passed%20by%20Parliament%20this%20month%2C%20with%20the%20opposition%20declaring%20the%20latter%20has%20been%20designed%20to%20rob%20Muslims%20of%20their%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EOver%20The%20Constitution...%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20battle%20over%20the%20Constitution%20carries%20over%20from%20the%20opposition's%20attacks%20last%20year%20while%20campaigning%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%20The%20Congress%20and%20other%20parties%20repeatedly%20claimed%20the%20BJP's%20'abki%20baar%20400%20paar'%20target%20was%20a%20pretext%20to%20ensure%20it%20had%20votes%20to%20change%20the%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20laughed%20off%20those%20claims%2C%20pointing%20out%20it%20had%20the%20numbers%20even%20after%20victories%20in%20the%202014%20and%202019%20elections.%20The%20400-seat%20target%2C%20Amit%20Shah%20said%2C%20was%20simply%20to%20expand%20its%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20votes%20were%20counted%2C%20the%20BJP%20fell%20well%20short%20of%20its%20target%3B%20in%20fact%20the%20party%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%20since%20it%20came%20to%20power%20in%202014%2C%20did%20not%20have%20a%20solo%20mandate%20to%20form%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20setback%20stung%20the%20BJP%2C%20particularly%20since%20it%20meant%20it%20needed%20support%20from%20Bihar%20Chief%20Minister%20Nitish%20Kumar's%20JDU%20and%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20N%20Chandrababu%20Naidu's%20TDP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20with%20elections%20this%20year%20in%20Bihar%20-%20a%20state%20with%20significant%20Dalit%20and%20Muslim%20populations%2C%20according%20to%20the%202023%20caste%20survey%20-%20Mr%20Modi's%20party%20is%20determined%20to%20avoid%20a%20re-run%2C%20or%20risk%20losing%20sway%20among%20groups%20that%2C%20together%2C%20make%20up%20over%2030%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHence%20the%20PM's%20focused%20attacks%20today%20on%20the%20Congress%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bdestroyer%20of%20Constitutions%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20is%20unlikely%20to%20let%20go%20of%20this%20issue%2C%20with%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20warning%20voters%20%26quot%3Bany%20weakening%20of%20the%20Constitution%20will%20directly%20impact%20the%20strength%20of%20India's%20democracy%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EAfter%20Bihar%202025...%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Constitution%20as%20a%20battleground%20between%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Congress-led%20opposition%20isn't%20confined%20to%20the%20Bihar%20election%20later%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBengal%20-%20which%20the%20BJP%20is%20desperate%20to%20win%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%20ever%2C%20and%20so%20quench%20the%20growing%20challenge%20of%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20-%20will%20vote%20in%202026%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20-%20the%20BJP's%20undisputed%20bastion%20in%20recent%20years%20-%20will%20vote%20the%20following%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBengal%20and%20UP%20are%20home%20to%20large%20chunks%20of%20Dalit%20and%20Muslim%20populations%2C%20so%20outreach%20efforts%20today%20and%20over%20the%20next%20week%20will%20be%20expected%20to%20hold%20each%20political%20party%20in%20good%20stead%20when%20campaigning%20begins%20for%20these%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744622640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-01%2F2moa5tu8_br-ambedkar-statue-generic_625x300_02_January_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fambedkar-jayanti-news-dr-br-ambedkar-legacy-battle-bjp-congress-bjp-congress-et-al-in-bit-absurd-battle-to-claim-ambedkars-legacy-8160966%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BJP%20and%20the%20opposition%2C%20led%20by%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20of%20ex-UP%20Chief%20Minister%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%2C%20have%20gone%20head-to-head%20on%20Monday%20-%20on%20Ambedkar%20Jayanti%20-%20to%20claim%20the%20legacy%20of%20Dr%20BR%20Ambedkar%20for%20themselves.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fambedkar-jayanti-news-dr-br-ambedkar-legacy-battle-bjp-congress-bjp-congress-et-al-in-bit-absurd-battle-to-claim-ambedkars-legacy-8160966%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWhy%20Doesn't%20Congress%20Name%20Muslim%20Chief%26quot%3B%3A%20PM%20Modi's%20Dare%20During%20Waqf%20Attack%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20all-out%20attack%20on%20the%20Congress%20for%20its%20stand%20against%20the%20Waqf%20(Amendment)%20Act%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20today%20said%20the%20Congress%20has%20only%20appeased%20Muslim%20fundamentalists%20and%20its%20opposition%20to%20the%20new%20law%20proves%20this.%20He%20also%20questioned%20why%20the%20Congress%20does%20not%20name%20a%20Muslim%20president%20and%20reserve%2050%20per%20cent%20of%20its%20election%20tickets%20for%20Muslim%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20was%20speaking%20at%20the%20inauguration%20ceremony%20of%20Hisar%20airport%20in%20Haryana.%20He%20said%20the%20airport%20will%20be%20a%20significant%20milestone%20in%20the%20state's%20development%20journey.%20Remembering%20BR%20Ambedkar%20on%20his%20birth%20anniversary%2C%20Dalit%20icon%20and%20the%20Constitution's%20architect%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20Dr%20Ambedkar's%20struggle%20inspires%20his%20government.%20%26quot%3BEvery%20decision%20and%20policy%20is%20dedicated%20to%20Babasahed%20Ambedkar%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETargeting%20the%20Congress%2C%20he%20said%20the%20Opposition%20party%20made%20the%20Constitution%20a%20tool%20for%20gaining%20power.%20%26quot%3BDuring%20the%20Emergency%2C%20the%20spirit%20of%20the%20Constitution%20was%20killed%20to%20retain%20power.%20The%20Constitution%20talks%20about%20a%20secular%20civil%20code%2C%20but%20Congress%20never%20implemented%20it.%20Today%2C%20a%20uniform%20civil%20code%20has%20been%20implemented%20in%20Uttarakhand.%20Unfortunately%2C%20the%20Congress%20is%20opposing%20this.%20Congress%20never%20bothered%20to%20check%20if%20the%20benefits%20of%20reservation%20reached%20SC%2FST%20and%20OBC%20communities%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20must%20never%20forget%20what%20the%20Congress%20did%20to%20Babasaheb%20Ambedkar.%20While%20he%20was%20alive%2C%20the%20party%20insulted%20him%20repeatedly.%20They%20made%20him%20lose%20elections%20twice.%20Congress%20wanted%20to%20uproot%20him%3B%20they%20conspired%20to%20keep%20him%20out%20of%20the%20system.%20After%20his%20death%2C%20they%20even%20tried%20to%20erase%20his%20memory.%20Babasaheb%20stood%20for%20equality%2C%20but%20Congress%20spread%20the%20virus%20of%20vote-bank%20politics%20throughout%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20BR%20Ambedkar%20had%20ruled%20out%20reservation%20on%20religious%20grounds.%20%26quot%3BCongress's%20appeasement%20politics%20has%20harmed%20the%20Muslims%20too.%20Congress%20has%20only%20made%20some%20fundamentalists%20happy.%20The%20rest%20of%20the%20society%20remained%20uneducated%20and%20poor.%20The%20biggest%20proof%20of%20this%20wrong%20approach%20is%20in%20the%20Waqf%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20made%20arbitrary%20changes%20in%20the%20Waqf%20law%20for%20political%20mileage%20and%20the%20changes%20turned%20the%20Constitution%20on%20its%20head%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20ask%20these%20vote-bank%20hungry%20leaders%2C%20if%20you%20care%20about%20the%20Muslims%2C%20why%20doesn't%20Congress%20make%20a%20Muslim%20its%20party%20president.%20Give%2050%20per%20cent%20tickets%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20to%20Muslims.%20If%20they%20win%2C%20they%20would%20put%20forward%20their%20views.%20But%20no%2C%20they%20won't%20give%20(Muslims)%20anything%20in%20the%20Congress.%20They%20will%20snatch%20the%20rights%20of%20citizens.%20Their%20intention%20was%20never%20to%20do%20anything%20good%20for%20anyone%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20lakhs%20of%20hectares%20of%20land%20are%20Waqf%20property.%20%26quot%3BIf%20Waqf%20properties%20had%20been%20used%20honestly%2C%20Muslim%20youths%20wouldn't%20need%20to%20earn%20a%20livelihood%20from%20repairing%20bicycle%20punctures.%20But%20only%20a%20few%20land%20mafia%20benefited%20from%20these%20properties.%20This%20mafia%20was%20looting%20lands%20belonging%20to%20Dalit%2C%20backward%20sections%20and%20widows.%20The%20loot%20of%20the%20poor%20will%20stop%20after%20these%20changes%20to%20the%20Waqf%20law.%20Under%20the%20new%20Waqf%20law%2C%20land%20or%20property%20belonging%20to%20tribals%20cannot%20be%20touched%20by%20the%20Waqf%20Board.%20Poor%20Muslims%20and%20Pasmanda%20Muslims%20will%20get%20their%20rights.%20This%20is%20real%20social%20justice%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHitting%20back%20at%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20said%20BR%20Ambedkar%20always%20stressed%20the%20importance%20of%20education.%20The%20government%2C%20he%20said%2C%20does%20not%20work%20on%20Dr%20Ambedkar's%20vision%2C%20but%20makes%20tall%20claims.%20%26quot%3BThey%20(BJP)%20only%20speak%20against%20Congress%2C%20Nehru%20ji%20and%20all%20we%20have%20done%20until%20now.%20But%2C%20I%20ask%20what%20have%20they%20done%20till%20now%20and%20which%20of%20Babasaheb's%20principles%20have%20they%20adopted%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20Women's%20Reservation%20Act%2C%20which%20mandates%2033%20per%20cent%20reservation%20of%20women%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20state%20Assemblies%2C%20Mr%20Kharge%20said%2C%20When%20the%20Women's%20Reservation%20Bill%20was%20passed%202%20years%20ago%2C%20the%20Congress%20demanded%20that%20it%20be%20implemented%20immediately.%20Our%20demand%20was%20that%20SC%2C%20ST%20and%20OBC%20women%20be%20given%20reservation%20in%20it.%20This%20is%20our%20objective.%20We%20have%20been%20fighting%20for%20this%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20(BJP)%20say%20we%20have%20insulted%20Babasaheb%20%C2%A0Ambedkar.%20Which%20party%20made%20Babasaheb%20%C2%A0Ambedkar%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly%20and%20Chairman%20of%20the%20Drafting%20Committee%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20Congress%20chief%20asked.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744622580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2Fu0ej9pnc_pm-modi_625x300_14_April_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-changed-waqf-rules-for-own-benefit-pm-modi-at-haryana-rally-8159594%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BCongress%20Changed%20Waqf%20Rules%20For%20Own%20Benefit%26quot%3B%3A%20PM%20Modi%20At%20Haryana%20Rally%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-changed-waqf-rules-for-own-benefit-pm-modi-at-haryana-rally-8159594%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22PNB%20scam%3A%20How%20Mehul%20Choksi%20was%20tracked%20down%20and%20arrested%20in%20Belgium%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22publishe