sion%20v.%20Meta%20Platforms%2C%20the%20FTC%20says%20the%20social%20media%20giant%20boxed%20out%20competitors.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMeta%20argues%20that%20it%20is%20a%20source%20of%20innovation%20and%20has%20not%20violated%20US%20antitrust%20laws.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20is%20set%20to%20face%20off%20against%20the%20Federal%20Trade%20Commission%20on%20Monday%20in%20what%20could%20be%20one%20of%20the%20most%20consequential%20antitrust%20trials%20in%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20FTC's%20case%20against%20Meta%20comes%20after%20a%20yearslong%20probe%20into%20whether%20the%20social%20media%20behemoth%20violated%20US%20competition%20laws%20when%20it%20acquired%20Instagram%20and%20WhatsApp.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20trial%2C%20FTC%20regulators%20want%20to%20force%20Meta%20to%20spin%20off%20the%20two%20services.%20If%20it%20succeeds%2C%20it%20would%20be%20a%20major%20blow%20to%20Meta's%20business.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EInstagram%20and%20WhatsApp%20both%20have%20over%202%20billion%20active%20users%2C%20according%20to%20the%20latest%20available%20data%20from%20those%20companies.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAttorneys%20for%20the%20FTC%20and%20Meta%20will%20offer%20their%20opening%20statements%20before%20Judge%20James%20Boasberg%20of%20the%20US%20District%20Court%20for%20the%20District%20of%20Columbia%20in%20a%20trial%20that%20begins%20today%20and%20is%20expected%20to%20last%20seven%20to%20eight%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20plans%20to%20call%20Meta%20CEO%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%20and%20former%20Meta%20Chief%20Operating%20Officer%20Sheryl%20Sandberg%20to%20the%20witness%20stand%2C%20along%20with%20Adam%20Mosseri%2C%20the%20head%20of%20Instagram.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20FTC%20argues%20that%20Meta's%202012%20acquisition%20of%20Instagram%20and%20its%202014%20acquisition%20of%20WhatsApp%20were%20intended%20to%20box%20out%20competition%20and%20dominate%20the%20social%20media%20sphere.%20The%20government%20says%20these%20acquisitions%20were%20part%20of%20Meta's%20%26quot%3Bbuy%20or%20bury%26quot%3B%20plan%20to%20maintain%20market%20dominance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERegulators%20say%20Meta's%20business%20strategy%20breaches%20existing%20antitrust%20laws%2C%20and%20the%20FTC%20is%20hoping%20to%20force%20Meta%20to%20divest%20both%20Instagram%20and%20WhatsApp%20to%20ease%20the%20company's%20grip%20on%20the%20industry%20and%20afford%20smaller%20companies%20the%20opportunities%20to%20attract%20more%20users%20and%20potential%20advertising%20dollars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20argues%20that%20the%20company%20has%20been%20a%20fair%20actor%20and%20a%20beacon%20of%20innovation%20in%20the%20social%20media%20marketplace.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20evidence%20at%20trial%20will%20show%20what%20every%2017-year-old%20in%20the%20world%20knows%3A%20Instagram%2C%20Facebook%2C%20and%20WhatsApp%20compete%20with%20Chinese-owned%20TikTok%2C%20YouTube%2C%20X%2C%20iMessage%2C%20and%20many%20others%2C%26quot%3B%20Meta%20spokesperson%20Christopher%20Sgro%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20%26quot%3BMore%20than%2010%20years%20after%20the%20FTC%20reviewed%20and%20cleared%20our%20acquisitions%2C%20the%20Commission's%20action%20in%20this%20case%20sends%20the%20message%20that%20no%20deal%20is%20ever%20truly%20final.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20first%20began%20at%20the%20end%20of%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20first%20term%20in%202020%20and%20forged%20ahead%20under%20former%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20antitrust%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-comments-about-facebook-mark-zuckerberg-feud-history-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edynamic%20between%20Trump%20and%20Zuckerberg%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20shifted%20demonstrably%20since%202020%2C%20however.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20Capitol%20riot%20on%20January%206%2C%202021%2C%20Trump%20railed%20against%20Meta's%20decision%20to%20%26quot%3Bindefinitely%26quot%3B%20suspend%20his%20Facebook%20account.%20In%20January%202023%2C%20Meta%20reins