st%20month%20or%20so%2C%20Microsoft%20has%20also%20deferred%20and%20canceled%20existing%20data%20center%20leases%20in%20the%20US%20and%20Europe%2C%20Elias%20wrote%20in%20a%20recent%20note%20to%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20pullback%20on%20new%20capacity%20leasing%20was%20largely%20driven%20by%20Microsoft's%20decision%20to%20not%20support%20incremental%20OpenAI%20training%20workloads%2C%20Elias%20said.%20A%20recent%20change%20to%20this%20crucial%20partnership%20allows%20OpenAI%20to%20work%20with%20other%20cloud%20providers%20beyond%20Microsoft.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20we%20continue%20to%20believe%20the%20lease%20cancellations%20and%20deferrals%20of%20capacity%20point%20to%20data%20center%20oversupply%20relative%20to%20its%20current%20demand%20forecast%2C%26quot%3B%20Elias%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20worrying%20because%20trillions%20of%20dollars%20in%20current%20and%20planned%20investments%20are%20riding%20on%20the%20generative%20AI%20boom%20continuing%20at%20a%20rapid%20pace.%20With%20so%20much%20money%20on%20the%20line%2C%20any%20inkling%20that%20this%20rocket%20ship%20is%20not%20ascending%20at%20light%20speed%20is%20unnerving.%20(I%20asked%20a%20Microsoft%20spokesperson%20all%20about%20this%20twice%2C%20and%20didn't%20get%20a%20response.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f97ade40-c374-413d-9a44-2427b655a0b1%5C%22%3EAn%20AI%20recalibration%2C%20not%20a%20retreat%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20reality%20is%20more%20nuanced%20than%20a%20simple%20pullback%2C%20though.%20What%20we're%20witnessing%20is%20a%20recalibration%20%E2%80%94%20not%20a%20retreat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBarclays%20analyst%20Raimo%20Lenschow%20put%20the%20situation%20in%20context.%20The%20initial%20wave%20of%20this%20industry%20spending%20spree%20focused%20a%20lot%20on%20securing%20land%20and%20buildings%20to%20house%20all%20the%20chips%20and%20other%20computing%20gear%20needed%20to%20create%20and%20run%20AI%20models%20and%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20this%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-data-centers-land-grab-google-meta-openai-amazon-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20%26quot%3Bland%20grab%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20it's%20common%20for%20large%20cloud%20companies%20to%20sign%20and%20negotiate%20leases%20that%20they%20end%20up%20walking%20away%20from%20later%2C%20Lenschow%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20that%20Microsoft%20feels%20more%20comfortable%20with%20the%20amount%20of%20land%20it%20has%20on%20hand%2C%20the%20company%20is%20likely%20shifting%20some%20spending%20to%20the%20later%20stages%20that%20focus%20more%20on%20buying%20the%20GPUs%20and%20other%20computing%20gear%20that%20go%20inside%20these%20new%20data%20centers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20other%20words%2C%20over%20the%20past%20few%20quarters%2C%20Microsoft%20has%20'overspent'%20on%20land%20and%20buildings%2C%20but%20is%20now%20going%20back%20to%20a%20more%20normal%20cadence%2C%26quot%3B%20Lenschow%20wrote%20in%20a%20recent%20note%20to%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%20still%20plans%20%2480%20billion%20in%20capital%20expenditures%20during%20its%202025%20fiscal%20year%20and%20has%20guided%20for%20year-over-year%20growth%20in%20the%20next%20fiscal%20year.%20So%2C%20the%20company%20probably%20isn't%20backing%20away%20from%20AI%20much%2C%20but%20rather%20becoming%20more%20strategic%20about%20where%20and%20how%20it%20invests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ed20c152-9a80-4918-9dfb-493aae9abdff%5C%22%3EFrom%20AI%20training%20to%20inference%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPart%20of%20the%20shift%20appears%20to%20be%20from%20AI%20training%20to%20inference.%20Pre-training%20is%20how%20new%20models%20are%20created%2C%20and%20this%20requires%20loads%20of%20closely%20connected%20GPUs%2C%20along%20with%20state-of-the-art%20networking.%20Expensive%20stuff!%20Inference%20is%20how%20existing%20models%20are%20run%20to%20support%20services%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-copilot-ai%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20agents%20and%20Copilots%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Inference%20is%20less%20technically%20demanding%20but%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20the%20larger%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20inference%20outpacing%20training%2C%20the%20focus%20is%20shifting%20toward%20scalable%2C%20cost-effective%20infrastructure%20that%20maximizes%20return%20on%20investment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20at%20a%20recent%20AI%20conference%20in%20New%20York%2C%20the%20discussion%20was%20focused%20more%20on%20efficiency%20rather%20than%20attaining%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fagi-predictions-looking-stretched-openai-sam-altman-google-ai-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAGI%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20artificial%20general%20intelligence%2C%20a%20costly%20endeavor%20to%20make%20machines%20work%20better%20than%20humans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20startup%20Cohere%20noted%20that%20its%20new%20Command%20A%20model%20only%20needs%20two%20GPUs%20to%20run.%20That's%20a%20heck%20of%20a%20lot%20less%20than%20most%20models%20have%20required%20in%20recent%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ea468866-bc1d-4ebe-b348-47853f10e3d7%5C%22%3EMicrosoft's%20AI%20chief%20weighs%20in%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-mustafa-suleyman-ai-copilot-update-reviews-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMustafa%20Suleyman%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20CEO%20of%20Microsoft%20AI%2C%20echoed%20this%20in%20a%20recent%20podcast.%20While%20he%20acknowledged%20a%20slight%20slowdown%20in%20returns%20from%20massive%20pre-training%20runs%2C%20he%20emphasized%20that%20the%20company's%20compute%20consumption%20is%20still%20%26quot%3Bunbelievable%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20just%20shifting%20to%20different%20stages%20of%20the%20AI%20pipeline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuleyman%20also%20clarified%20that%20some%20of%20the%20canceled%20leases%20and%20projects%20were%20never%20finalized%20contracts%2C%20but%20rather%20exploratory%20discussions%20%E2%80%94%20part%20of%20standard%20operating%20procedure%20in%20hyperscale%20cloud%20planning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20strategic%20pivot%20comes%20as%20OpenAI%2C%20Microsoft's%20close%20partner%2C%20has%20begun%20sourcing%20capacity%20from%20other%20cloud%20providers%2C%20and%20is%20even%20hinting%20at%20developing%20its%20own%20data%20centers.%20Microsoft%2C%20however%2C%20maintains%20a%20right%20of%20first%20refusal%20on%20new%20OpenAI%20capacity%2C%20signaling%20continued%20deep%20integration%20between%20the%20two%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226c84ff61-bf1e-49cc-9898-b28f188b7b3f%5C%22%3EWhat%20does%20this%20all%20mean%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20don't%20mistake%20agility%20for%20weakness.%20Microsoft%20is%20likely%20adjusting%20to%20changing%20market%20dynamics%2C%20not%20scaling%20back%20ambition.%20Second%2C%20the%20hyperscaler%20space%20remains%20incredibly%20competitive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Elias%2C%20when%20Microsoft%20walked%20away%20from%20capacity%20in%20overseas%20markets%2C%20Google%20stepped%20in%20to%20snap%20up%20the%20supply.%20Meanwhile%2C%20Meta%20backfilled%20the%20capacity%20that%20Microsoft%20left%20on%20the%20table%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBoth%20of%20these%20hyperscalers%20are%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20a%20material%20year-over-year%20ramp%20in%20data%20center%20demand%2C%26quot%3B%20Elias%20wrote%2C%20referring%20to%20Google%20and%20Meta.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20Microsoft's%20pivot%20may%20be%20more%20a%20sign%20of%20maturity%2C%20than%20retreat.%20As%20AI%20adoption%20enters%20its%20next%20phase%2C%20the%20winners%20won't%20necessarily%20be%20those%20who%20spend%20the%20most%20%E2%80%94%20but%20those%20who%20spend%20the%20smartest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-ai-data-center-cloud-decreased-spending-explained-why-2025-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744621321000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67fbcf19c6ad288d147e08e7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-ai-data-center-cloud-decreased-spending-explained-why-2025-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Microsoft's%20decision%20to%20pace%20data%20center%20growth%20indicates%20a%20shift%20from%20AI%20training%20to%20inference%2C%20aligning%20with%20the%20industry's%20embrace%20of%20efficiency.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22abarr%40businessinsider.com%20(Alistair%20Barr)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A204%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-ai-data-center-cloud-decreased-spending-explained-why-2025-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22AI%20is%20coming%20for%20the%20NSFW%20emoji%20chain%20text%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22iPhone%20screen%20displaying%20a%20text%20message%20thread%20with%20a%20lengthy%2C%20emoji-filled%20message%20discussing%20the%20new%20trade%20tariffs.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f7fe3ea466d2b74ab2d3de%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EEmojipasta%3B%20Alyssa%20Powell%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EEmojipasta%20are%20silly%2C%20innuendo-laded%20texts%20often%20sent%20as%20a%20chain.%20They're%20full%20of%20NSFW%20emojis%20%E2%80%94%20and%20popular.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThey're%20hard%20to%20make%20yourself%2C%20but%20AI%20tools%20can%20create%20them%20easily.%20Does%20that%20make%20them%20lose%20something%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BA%20computer%20will%20never%20feel%20rage.%20A%20computer%20will%20never%20feel%20horny%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20Redditor%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20AI%20continues%20to%20make%20breakthroughs%20in%20live-saving%20medicine%20and%20anime%20facsimile%2C%20it%20threatens%20one%20of%20the%20greatest%20new%20art%20forms%20that%20has%20developed%20this%20century%3A%20the%20NSFW%20emoji%20chain%20text.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20some%20context%20in%20case%20you've%20never%20been%20sent%20one%20of%20these.%20This%20is%20the%20start%20of%20a%20rare%20safe-for-work%20example%20about%20the%20EZ-Pass%20scam%20texts%20that%20have%20been%20going%20around%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3E%E2%80%BC%EF%B8%8F%E2%80%BC%EF%B8%8F%F0%9F%9A%A8%F0%9F%9A%A8%F0%9F%98%B1E-ZPASS%20%F0%9F%98%8C%F0%9F%98%B5%20FINAL%20%F0%9F%8E%AC%F0%9F%98%A9%F0%9F%92%A6%E2%9D%8C%20%E2%9D%8CREMINDER%E2%8F%B0%E2%8F%B0%E2%8F%B0%F0%9F%9A%A8%3A%20YOU%F0%9F%AB%B5%F0%9F%AB%B5%F0%9F%98%89HAVE%20%F0%9F%A7%90AN%20OUTSTANDING%20%F0%9F%A5%B3%F0%9F%A4%A9%F0%9F%91%80%F0%9F%98%A9TOLL%E2%80%BC%EF%B8%8F%F0%9F%9A%A8%F0%9F%92%B0%F0%9F%92%B0%F0%9F%9A%97%F0%9F%9A%98%E2%80%BC%EF%B8%8F%E2%80%BC%EF%B8%8F%F0%9F%9A%A8%F0%9F%9A%A8%F0%9F%98%B3%F0%9F%98%B3%F0%9F%98%A2%F0%9F%98%AD%20YOUR%20TOLL%20%F0%9F%9A%97%F0%9F%AB%A8%20ACCOUNT%20%F0%9F%92%B2%F0%9F%92%B0%F0%9F%A7%BE%F0%9F%A7%BEBALANCE%F0%9F%A7%98%E2%80%8D%E2%99%80%EF%B8%8F%E2%9A%96%EF%B8%8F%E2%9A%96%EF%B8%8F%20IS%20%F0%9F%A4%A8%F0%9F%A4%94%F0%9F%A7%90OUTSTANDING%20%F0%9F%98%A9%F0%9F%AB%A8%F0%9F%AB%A8%E2%80%BC%EF%B8%8F%E2%80%BC%EF%B8%8F%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20goes%20on%20from%20there%2C%20but%20we'll%20cut%20it%20off%20for%20a%20family-friendly%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20emojipasta%20texts%20are%20like%20chain%20letters%2C%20in%20theory.%20They're%20full%20of%20emojis%20and%20usually%20sexualized%20language.%20They're%20meant%20to%20be%20funny%2C%20not%20actually%20sexy.%20(I%20don't%20think%20anyone%20is%20sending%20these%20to%20someone%20they%20intend%20to%20seduce%20(if%20you%20somehow%20have%2C%20congrats%20to%20you).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theatlantic.com%2Ftechnology%2Farchive%2F2020%2F01%2Fhistory-emoji-chain-texts%2F605272%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWhy%20do%20these%20exist%2C%20and%20where%20did%20they%20originate%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%20Well%2C%20they're%20funny%2C%20so%20that's%20the%20why.%20And%20while%20the%20origins%20aren't%20clear%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20them%20seem%20to%20come%20from%20Reddit's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2Femojipasta%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Er%2Femojipasta%3C%2Fa%3E%20(based%20on%20the%20term%20%26quot%3Bcopypasta%2C%26quot%3B%20internet%20slang%20for%20a%20text%20that%20gets%20passed%20around%20and%20copied).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20emojipasta%20subreddit%20is%20updated%20nearly%20daily%20%E2%80%94%20most%20are%20related%20to%20minor%20holidays%20or%20events%2C%20or%20sometimes%20based%20on%20requests%20for%20someone%20to%20make%20something%20new.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20a%20recent%20one%20celebrating%20the%20Ides%20of%20March%20included%20the%20line%2C%20%26quot%3BCaesar%F0%9F%A5%97%20said%20'et%20tu%2C%20BOOTEH%F0%9F%A5%BA%2C'%20before%20he%20SASHAYED%20AWAY%F0%9F%92%83%20from%20life%F0%9F%AA%A6!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20emojipasta%20about%20the%20new%20trade%20tariffs%20ended%20with%20a%20warning%3A%20%26quot%3BSEND%20%E2%9C%89%EF%B8%8F%20THIS%20TO%2010%20PATRIOTIC%20THICC%20%F0%9F%8D%91%20TRADE%20WARRIORS%20%F0%9F%A5%B5%F0%9F%92%AA%20AND%20YOU'LL%20GET%20A%20TAX%20CUT%20%F0%9F%92%B5%E2%9C%A8.%20IGNORE%20IT%2C%20AND%20YOU'LL%20PAY%20DOUBLE%20AT%20THE%20STORE%20%F0%9F%9B%8D%EF%B8%8F%F0%9F%98%B1%E2%80%BC%EF%B8%8F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20actually%20tried%20writing%20my%20own%20for%20events%20or%20inside%20jokes%20with%20friends.%20It's%20genuinely%20hard!%20I%20found%20myself%20copying%20aspects%20of%20other%20chain%20texts%20to%20get%20inspiration%20about%20where%20to%20put%20the%20%F0%9F%8D%91%20emojis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhich%20is%20why%20these%20are%20a%20perfect%20place%20for%20AI%20to%20come%20in%3A%20The%20subreddit%20suggested%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Femoji-pasta-maker.fly.dev%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEmoji%20Pasta%20Generator%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20made%20by%20New%20York-based%20engineer%20Abhishyant%20Khare.%20The%20sparse%20webpage%20asks%20for%20a%20topic%20and%20then%20can%20reliably%20spit%20out%20an%20actually%20pretty%20good%20suggestive%20emoji%20pasta.%20(I%20tested%20it%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20really%20good.)%20Khare%20also%20made%20an%20iMessage%20extension.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20friends%20and%20I%20were%20discussing%20who%20would%20be%20replaced%20by%20AI%20first%20as%20a%20joke%2C%20and%20then%20my%20friend%20Vivek%20sent%20one%20of%20these%20texts%20in%20our%20group%20chat%2C%26quot%3B%20Khare%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BI%20realized%20I%20could%20probably%20replace%20Vivek%20with%20AI%20since%20he%20mostly%20just%20sends%20these%20types%20of%20texts%2C%20and%20got%20to%20work%20building%20the%20emoji%20pasta%20maker%2C%20and%20the%20rest%20is%20history.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bdfd0abc-1711-4a1b-ba8c-f6dfe20d1b37%5C%22%3EBut%20does%20using%20AI%20take%20the%20fun%20out%20of%20it%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESeems%20like%20a%20smart%20use%20of%20AI%2C%20but%20are%20there%20ethical%20considerations%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20this%20suggestive%20art%20form%3F%20(And%20does%20having%20a%20computer%20generate%20it%20just%20take%20some%20of%20the%20fun%20out%20of%20it%20all%3F)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20asked%20the%20moderators%20of%20r%2Femojipasta%20what%20they%20thought%20about%20AI-generated%20texts%20and%20whether%20they%20were%20even%20allowed%20on%20the%20subreddit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20discussed%20banning%20AI-generated%20content%20in%20here%20because%2C%20frankly%2C%20it%20seems%20lazy%20to%20use%20a%20bot%20instead%20of%20writing%20it%20yourself%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Drew%20Robinson%2C%20one%20of%20r%2Femojipasta's%20moderators.%20%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20so%20far%2C%20we%20haven't%20seen%20the%20need%20to%20outright%20ban%20it%20as%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20AI-generated%20content%20gets%20downvoted%20because%20frankly%2C%20it%20sucks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERobinson%20conceded%20that%20some%20posts%20on%20the%20subreddit%20were%20probably%20made%20by%20AI%20and%20had%20even%20managed%20to%20get%20some%20upvotes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20still%20a%20strong%20tradition%20of%20human-crafted%20emojipasta.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20Bailey%2C%20a%2028-year-old%20from%20the%20Seatle%20area%2C%20noticed%20the%20subreddit%20didn't%20have%20a%20good%20chain%20text%20to%20celebrate%20the%20Seattle%20Mariners%20baseball%20season%20opening%20day%20and%20was%20determined%20to%20make%20one%20himself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBailey%20(who%20requested%20not%20to%20use%20his%20last%20name%20so%20that%20he%20is%20not%20forever%20associated%20on%20the%20internet%20with%20baseball-related%20smut)%20did%20it%20the%20truly%20old-fashioned%20way%2C%20with%20a%20pencil%20and%20paper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThought%20about%20an%20overall%20MLB%20one%2C%20but%20knew%20more%20jokes%20I%20could%20make%20with%20the%20Mariners%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BDid%20a%20first%20draft%20on%20a%20price%20of%20paper%20then%20showed%20a%20couple%20of%20my%20friends%20who%20suggested%20edits%20and%20helped%20add%20the%20emojis.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20browsed%20through%20the%20subreddit%2C%20I%20started%20to%20notice%20some%20patterns.%20Some%20posts%20had%20the%20hallmarks%20of%20ChatGPT%20%E2%80%94%20the%20use%20of%20bullet%20points%2C%20or%20ones%20that%20merely%20interspersed%20emojis%20through%20an%20otherwise%20normal%20sentence%2C%20lacking%20the%20erratic%20capitalization%20and%20ribald%20puns%20that%20truly%20suggestive%20chain%20texts%20have.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBailey's%20filthy%20Mariner's%20post%20stood%20out%20to%20me%20as%20particularly%20human%20%E2%80%94%20creative%2C%20suggestive%2C%20making%20full%20use%20of%20baseball-related%20innuendo%2C%20and%20full%20of%20emojis.%20It%20was%20somehow%20even%20more%20filthy%20than%20one%20a%20few%20days%20later%20about%20Hooters%20filing%20for%20bankruptcy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2242021e48-3b46-4000-ac85-6dac30f5b4c6%5C%22%3ESomething's%20lost%20with%20bot-written%20NSFW%20text%20chains%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20theory%2C%20these%20emojipasta%20are%20perfect%20for%20AI%20%E2%80%94%20they're%20labor-intensive%20and%20annoying%20for%20humans%20to%20do%20(finding%20all%20the%20emojis%20in%20your%20keyboard%20is%20a%20pain!)%2C%20have%20a%20reliably%20predictable%20tone%20and%20verbiage%2C%20and%20rely%20on%20general%20knowledge%20of%20current%20and%20historical%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20yet%2C%20it%20does%20seem%20something%20is%20lost%20if%20it's%20AI-written.%20For%20me%2C%20part%20of%20the%20humor%20is%20just%20knowing%20that%20someone%20spent%20time%20writing%20these%20%E2%80%94%20the%20%26quot%3BI%20can't%20believe%20someone%20%3Cem%3Edid%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%26quot%3B%20factor.%20Knowing%20it's%20as%20easy%20as%20a%20few%20words%20in%20a%20prompt%20box%20takes%20the%20magic%20out%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Robinson%2C%20it's%20more%20existential%3A%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20like%20these%20are%20particularly%20high-brow%20pieces%20of%20art%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20a%20computer%20will%20never%20feel%20rage.%20A%20computer%20will%20never%20feel%20horny.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnswfw-emoji-text-chain-emojipasta-ai-written-reddit-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744621261000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f7fe3ea466d2b74ab2d3de%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnswfw-emoji-text-chain-emojipasta-ai-written-reddit-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Silly%2C%20risqu%C3%A9%20chain%20texts%20are%20being%20generated%20by%20AI.%20But%20some%20connoisseurs%20of%20the%20modern%20art%20form%20don't%20like%20it%20at%20all.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22knotopoulos%40businessinsi