IA%20is%20a%20clinical%20research%20company.%20For%20decades%2C%20it%20has%20conducted%20clinical%20trial%20research%20for%20the%20pharmaceutical%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20means%20they're%20working%20inside%20healthcare%20systems%2C%20as%20you're%20doing%20trials%2C%20you're%20collecting%20all%20this%20information%20about%20patients%20and%20their%20electronic%20health%20records%2C%20their%20labs%2C%20their%20imaging%2C%20what%20they%20ate%20for%20breakfast%20%E2%80%94%20that%20kind%20of%20stuff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey've%20essentially%20created%20a%20data%20network%20because%20they%20serve%2010s%20of%201000s%20of%20customers.%20So%20they%20have%20a%20data%20network%20that%20now%20all%20of%20a%20sudden%20can%20get%20an%20agentic%20AI%20%E2%80%94%20an%20intelligence%20layer%20%E2%80%94%20put%20on%20top%20of%20it%20to%20start%20offering%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20they've%20done%20in%20the%20past%20is%20taken%20their%20data%20and%20they've%20sold%20it%20to%20Company%20A%2C%20Company%20B%2C%20and%20Company%20C%2C%20so%20that%20A%2C%20B%2C%20and%20C%20would%20take%20it%20in-house%20and%20try%20to%20build%20their%20own%20intelligence%20layer%20on%20top%2C%20recreating%20the%20wheel%20at%20every%20single%20one%20and%20doing%20it%20for%20different%20purposes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20now%20have%20an%20opportunity%20to%20take%20a%20very%20pristine%20dataset%20and%20overlay%20an%20intelligence%20layer%20on%20it.%20IQVIA%20is%20like%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsap-restructuring-ai-business-strategy-8000-jobs-buyouts-software-cloud-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESAP%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgenerative-ai-evolution-software-companies-develop-ai-agents-workforce-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EServiceNow%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20healthcare%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20lot%20of%20the%20examples%20of%20AI%20in%20healthcare%20sound%20like%20they%20could%20change%20the%20costs.%20Imaging%20would%20have%20to%20be%20billed%20very%20differently%20if%20it%20was%20so%20ubiquitous%20in%20the%20way%20you're%20describing.%20Do%20you%20think%20about%20how%20the%20costs%20are%20going%20to%20shift%3F%20It%20feels%20like%20a%20pretty%20radical%20change.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20radical%20change%2C%20and%20it%20will%20take%20radical%20change%20across%20a%20very%20complicated%20economic%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20lots%20of%20conclusive%20evidence%20that%20if%20you%20catch%2C%20for%20example%2C%20some%20levels%20of%20cancer%20at%20stage%20one%20versus%20stage%20four%2C%20they're%20preventable%20and%20the%20cost%20to%20the%20system%20is%20drastically%20changed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20we're%20still%20in%20a%20very%20'treat%20the%20sick'%20rather%20than%20'keep%20them%20healthy'%20mode.%20If%20we%20could%20have%20systems%20that%20can%20catch%20things%20earlier%2C%20then%20that%20should%20create%20a%20calculation%20that%20would%20make%20a%20lot%20of%20sense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EI'm%20wondering%20if%20you%20spend%20any%20time%20talking%20to%20ordinary%20people%20about%20AI%20and%20healthcare.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYeah%2C%20I'm%20curious%20to%20know%20how%20people%20would%20interpret%20having%20a%20phone%20listen%20to%20their%20doctor%20because%2C%20on%20the%20one%20hand%2C%20they%20think%20about%20all%20these%20privacy%20concerns%2C%20but%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20when%20I%20explain%20the%20benefits%2C%20they%20realize%20%E2%80%94%20'Oh%20my%20God%2C%20that%20would%20change%20the%20experience%20forever%20for%20good.'%20It's%20just%2C%20sometimes%20it%20seems%20invasive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20they%20don't%20know%20the%2055%20positive%20byproducts%20of%20AI%20being%20in%20the%20system.%20I%20pretty%20much%20live%20and%20breathe%20healthcare.%20So%20I'm%20talking%20about%20it%20all%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20talking%20to%20my%209-year-old%20daughter%2C%20for%20e