in%20Cuba%2C%20suggesting%20he%20planned%20to%20move%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChoksi%2C%20however%2C%20alleged%20that%20Barbara%20did%20not%20try%20to%20help%20him%20when%20he%20was%20being%20beaten%20up%20and%20placed%20on%20a%20watercraft%20to%20be%20taken%20to%20Dominica%20from%20Antigua%20and%20Barbuda.%20He%20also%20said%20the%20way%20Barbara%20behaved%20indicated%20%26quot%3Bshe%20was%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20this%20whole%20plan%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPriti%20Choksi%20trashed%20Barbara's%20claims%20that%20she%20knew%20Choksi%20as%20Raj.%20%26quot%3BHow%20is%20it%20possible%20that%20despite%20all%20the%20media%20attention%20and%20public%20furore%20surrounding%20this%20case%2C%20that%20this%20lady%20who%20has%20an%20Instagram%20account%20with%20thousands%20of%20followers%20was%20in%20the%20dark%20about%20all%20this%2C%20and%20did%20not%20come%20out%20to%20speak%20in%20defence%20of%20her%20'friend'%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThese%20bogus%20claims%20are%20only%20an%20attempt%20to%20present%20a%20wrong%20picture%20of%20my%20husband%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChoksi%20was%20imprisoned%20in%20the%20Dominican%20Republic%20for%2051%20days%20before%20he%20got%20relief%20from%20the%20British%20Queen's%20Privy%20Council%20and%20returned%20to%20Antigua%2C%20foiling%20India's%20attempts%20to%20extradite%20him.%20Later%2C%20the%20illegal%20entry%20charges%20against%20him%20in%20the%20Dominican%20Republic%20were%20dropped.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20March%202023%2C%20Interpol%20took%20down%20a%20Red%20Notice%20against%20Choksi.%20A%20Red%20Notice%20is%20a%20request%20to%20law%20enforcement%20worldwide%20to%20locate%20and%20provisionally%20arrest%20a%20person%20pending%20extradition%20or%20surrender.%20In%20response%20to%20the%20Interpol%20move%2C%20the%20CBI%20said%20Choksi%20approached%20international%20forums%2C%20including%20the%20Commission%20for%20Control%20of%20Interpol's%20Files%2C%20with%20%26quot%3Bfalse%20claims%2C%20concocted%20dramatic%20stories%20and%20imaginary%20narratives%26quot%3B%20to%20%26quot%3Bcreate%20diversions%26quot%3B%20because%20he%20faces%20possibilities%20of%20extradition%20to%20India.%20The%20CBI%20had%20also%20said%20an%20INTERPOL%20Red%20Notice%20is%20%26quot%3Bneither%20a%20pre%20requisite%20nor%20a%20requirement%20for%20extradition%20proceedings%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20Indian%20agencies%20learned%20that%20Choksi%20was%20in%20Belgium%2C%20and%20they%20promptly%20alerted%20the%20agencies%20there.%20All%20documents%20regarding%20the%20fraud%20case%20were%20also%20shared.%20Belgian%20police%20arrested%20Choksi%20on%20Saturday%20and%20found%20he%20was%20trying%20to%20flee%20to%20Switzerland.%20Choksi's%20wife%20Priti%20is%20a%20Belgian%20citizen.%20According%20to%20reports%2C%20Choksi%20submitted%20fabricated%20documents%20to%20get%20a%20residency%20card%20in%20Belgium.%20He%20also%20concealed%20that%20he%20was%20a%20citizen%20of%20India%20and%20Antigua.%20Earlier%2C%20in%20February%2C%20Choksi's%20lawyer%20told%20a%20Mumbai%20court%20that%20he%20cannot%20return%20to%20India%20because%20he%20was%20in%20Belgium%20for%20blood%20cancer%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChoksi's%20lawyer%20said%20he%20will%20file%20an%20application%20in%20Belgium%2C%20seeking%20relief%20on%20health%20grounds.%20Vijay%20Aggarwal%20said%20a%20key%20ground%20for%20appeal%20will%20be%20Choksi's%20health.%20%26quot%3BHe%20is%20undergoing%20cancer%20treatment%20and%20wants%20to%20continue%20it%20in%20Switzerland.%20He%20is%20currently%20not%20a%20flight%20risk%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20The%20lawyer%20cited%20security%20concerns%20if%20Choksi%20is%20brought%20back%20to%20India.%20%26quot%3BWe%20believe%20that%20as%20soon%20as%20he%20arrives%2C%20he%20will%20receive%20inhuman%20treatment.%20He%20wants%20to%20protect%20himself%20from%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744620960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025