%202.4%20GW%20solar%20modules%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fjupiter-international-secures-500-cr-investment-to-boost-solar-capacity-125041400263_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Route%20To%20Green%20Card%20Gets%20Tougher%20For%20Immigrant%20Spouses%20Of%20US%20Citizens%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMarrying%20a%20US%20citizen%20or%20green%20card%20holder%20is%20no%20longer%20a%20smooth%20sailing%20one-way%20ride%20to%20the%20American%20dream%20for%20immigrants.%20Amid%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20crackdown%20on%20immigration%2C%20the%20American%20administration%20has%20adopted%20stricter%20policies%20to%20shape%20current%20immigration%20procedures--%20a%20stark%20contrast%20from%20Biden-era%20policies%2C%20when%20occasionally%20even%20waived%20off%20interviews%20of%20immigrant%20spouses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20marriage-based%20green%20card%20applications%20always%20included%20an%20interview%20stage%2C%20in%20recent%20months%2C%20a%20shift%20was%20witnessed%20with%20the%20administration%20adopting%20a%20more%20intense%20vetting%20process.%20Officials%20are%20requesting%20detailed%20documents%20outlining%20the%20minute%20aspects%20of%20relationships%2C%20including%20knowledge%20about%20the%20spouses'%20sleeping%20habits%20and%20allergies%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20by%20Times%20Of%20India%20(TOI).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%26quot%3BOfficers%20will%20be%20looking%20deeper...%20leaning%20into%20their%20discretion%20more%20often%20than%20they%20did%20in%20the%20Biden%20years.%20They%20are%20already%20spending%20more%20time%20verifying%20marriages%2C%20and%20we%20are%20seeing%20an%20increase%20in%20requests%20for%20evidence%2C%26quot%3B%20Ashwin%20Sharma%2C%20an%20immigration%20attorney%2C%20told%20TOI.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EVetting%20Process%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20key%20step%20to%20getting%20the%20green%20card%20clearance%20is%20tackling%20the%20interview.%20If%20the%20spouse%20applying%20for%20permanent%20residency%20resides%20outside%20America%2C%20the%20interview%20will%20be%20conducted%20by%20US%20consulate%20officials.%20Those%20already%20in%20the%20United%20States--%20like%20a%20non-immigrant%20H-1B%20visa%20--%20must%20apply%20for%20adjustment%20of%20status%2C%20with%20interviews%20carried%20out%20by%20the%20United%20States%20Citizenship%20and%20Immigration%20Services%20(USCIS).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImmigration%20lawyers%20cautioned%20applicants%20to%20expect%20detailed%20questioning%20and%20asked%20them%20to%20ensure%20all%20documents%20are%20in%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20seeing%20an%20increase%20in%20requests%20for%20evidence%2C%20and%20it's%20likely%20this%20pattern%20will%20soon%20become%20official%20policy%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20immigration%20attorney%20Sharma.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20experts%20said%20that%20consular%20officials%20are%20paying%20special%20attention%20to%20the%20couple's%20story%2C%20about%20how%20they%20met%2C%20their%20intention%20to%20live%20together%2C%20and%20how%20they%20have%20maintained%20the%20relationship.%20And%20since%20the%20US%20citizen%20spouses%20are%20not%20allowed%20to%20attend%20the%20visa%20interview%20in%20consular%20cases%2C%20the%20entire%20burden%20of%20proof%20lies%20on%20documents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDocuments%20have%20to%20tell%20the%20full%20story%3A%20how%20the%20relationship%20began%2C%20genuine%20intent%20to%20live%20a%20married%20life%20together%2C%20how%20it's%20been%20sustained%2C%20and%20why%20it%20is%20bona%20fide.%20That%20means%20clear%20evidence%20of%20communication%2C%20visits%2C%20shared%20plans%2C%20and%2For%20family%20involvement%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Can%20Be%20Considered%20Evidence%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESnehal%20Batra%2C%20managing%20attorney%20at%20NPZ%20Law%20Group%2C%20told%20TOI%20that%20applicants%20must%20be%20prepared%20with%20extensive%20documentation%2C%20which%20could%20include%20money%20transfer%20receipts%2C%20call%20logs%2C%20photos%2C%20joint%20accounts%2C%20and%20even%20joint%20life%20insurance%20policies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAdditionally%2C%20be%20prepared%20to%20answer%20questions%20about%20your%20marital%20relationship%2C%20including%20your%20spouse's%20current%20employment%2C%20salary%2C%20education%20and%20any%20prior%20marriages%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBatra%20cautioned%20that%20if%20a%20green%20card%20is%20%26quot%3Bdenied%20due%20to%20an%20alleged%20marriage%20fraud%2C%20the%20spouse%20can%20be%20placed%20in%20removal%20proceedings%20(deportation).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EBiden-Era%20Leniency%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Joe%20Biden%20last%20year%20unveiled%20new%20rules%20easing%20the%20process%20for%20undocumented%20spouses%20of%20US%20citizens%20to%20obtain%20permanent%20residency%20status.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20rules%20did%20not%20expand%20eligibility%20for%20permanent%20residency%2C%20but%20rather%20streamlined%20the%20process%20for%20those%20who%20already%20qualify.%20That%20includes%20removing%20a%20requirement%20that%20they%20leave%20the%20country%20as%20part%20of%20the%20application%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744617600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-04%2Fj8u2trc8_immigration-generic-afp-650_625x300_22_April_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftrump-immigration-crackdown-route-to-us-residency-gets-tougher-for-spouses-of-us-citizen-green-card-holders-8160404%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Marrying%20a%20US%20citizen%20or%20green%20card%20holder%20is%20no%20longer%20a%20smooth%20sailing%20one-way%20ride%20to%20the%20American%20dream%20for%20immigrants.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22cano