n%2C%20you%20know%2C%20improvise%20when%20needed'.%20Fortunately%2C%20everything%20came%20off%2C%20and%20I'm%20happy%20that%20I%20batted%20well.%20But%20again%2C%20I%20would%20have%20loved%20that%20if%20the%20team%20had%20gone%20on%20to%20win.%26quot%3B%20He%20didn't%20play%20in%20first%20four%20games%20but%20knew%20that%20sooner%20or%20later%20his%20chance%20would%20come%20and%20he%20would%20have%20to%20be%20ready.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLook%2C%20obviously%2C%20we%20lost%20an%20important%20player%20in%20Faf%2C%20and%20we%20always%20knew%20-%20the%20few%20of%20us%20batters%20who%20are%20sitting%20outside%20who%20should%20be%20and%20have%20to%20be%20ready%20at%20any%20given%20time.%20So%2C%20mentally%2C%20I%20was%20ready%2C%20and%20obviously%20looking%20forward%20to%20the%20chance%2C%20whenever%20it%20came%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BI%20felt%20confident.%20I%20felt%20like%2C%20I'm%20well%20prepared%20to%20play%20in%20the%20IPL%20if%20given%20the%20opportunity.%20So%20it%20was%20all%20about%20me%20preparing%20the%20way%20that%20I've%20been%20all%20through%20the%20season%20and%20waiting%20for%20my%20chance.%20So%20I%20was%20doing%20my%20bit%20to%20prepare%20and%20be%20ready%20for%20the%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20always%20a%20tough%20call%20for%20the%20team%20to%20pick%2011%20or%2012%20players%2C%20and%20I've%20always%20respected%20that.%20For%20me%2C%20it%20was%20about%20preparing%20and%20keeping%20the%20same%20process%20that%20I%20followed%2C%20which%20has%20worked%20for%20me%2C%20and%20just%20being%20ready%20to%20go%20out%20there%20and%20perform%20for%20the%20team.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20PTI%20Inputs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744615260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2Ft23l9mek_karun-nair-bcci_625x300_14_April_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2025%2Ftheres-no-value-for-me-karun-nairs-remarks-on-own-batting-sum-up-