aar%20and%20PAN%20made%20first%20and%20then%20apply%20for%20a%20passport.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaif%20Ali%20Khan%20was%20stabbed%20multiple%20times%20during%20a%20robbery%20attempt%20at%20his%20Bandra%20home%20on%20January%2016.%20Bleeding%20heavily%20from%20his%20injuries%2C%20the%20actor%20was%20rushed%20to%20Lilavati%20Hospital.%20He%20was%20discharged%20five%20days%20later.%20Police%20arrested%20Shehzad%20in%20Thane%20three%20days%20after%20the%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShehzad%20has%20told%20the%20police%20that%20he%20is%20from%20Jhalokathi%20district%20in%20Bangladesh%20and%20illegally%20entered%20India%20eight%20months%20before%20the%20robbery%20attempt.%20He%20stayed%20in%20Kolkata%20for%20about%2015%20days%20before%20travelling%20to%20Mumbai%20in%20the%20Gitanjali%20Express.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20worked%20at%20a%20hotel%20in%20Mumbai%20and%20took%20a%20day%20off%20on%20January%2015.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20not%20well%20and%20I%20needed%20to%20get%20a%20PAN%20card%20and%20Aadhaar%20card%20made%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20had%20spoken%20to%20someone%20who%20had%20asked%20for%20Rs%2030%2C000%20to%20get%20the%20fake%20documents%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShehzad%20told%20police%20that%20he%20had%20planned%20a%20%26quot%3Bsmall%20theft%26quot%3B%20that%20would%20help%20him%20get%20his%20documents%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Night%20Of%20Attack%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShehzad%20has%20told%20the%20cops%20that%20he%20went%20to%20the%20roof%20of%20a%20building%20adjoining%20the%20one%20in%20which%20Saif%20Ali%20Khan%20stayed.%20From%20there%2C%20he%20then%20jumped%20into%20the%20premises%20of%20the%20building%20where%20the%20actor%20stayed.%20He%20then%20went%20up%20the%20staircases%20on%20the%20rear%20side%20of%20the%20building%20till%20he%20found%20a%20security%20net.%20He%20used%20a%20cutter%20and%20gained%20access%20to%20the%20air%20conditioning%20duct.%20He%20then%20gained%20access%20to%20Mr%20Khan's%20home%20through%20the%20bathroom.%20%26quot%3BI%20saw%20a%20caregiver%20on%20her%20phone%20and%20another%20sleeping.%20A%20child%20(Jeh)%20was%20sleeping%20in%20the%20bed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20entered%20the%20house%2C%20the%20shocked%20nanny%20asked%20what%20he%20wanted.%20Shehzad%20demanded%20Rs%201%20crore.%20At%20this%20point%2C%20Mr%20Khan%20entered%20the%20room%20and%20grabbed%20him.%20%26quot%3BI%20stabbed%20him%20to%20escape.%20I%20stabbed%20him%20on%20his%20back%20and%20arms.%20Then%20his%20grip%20loosened.%20He%20pushed%20me%20into%20the%20room%20and%20locked%20the%20door.%20But%20I%20escaped%20through%20the%20window%20and%20used%20a%20pipe%20to%20climb%20down.%20I%20changed%20my%20clothes%20downstairs%20and%20fled%20to%20the%20bus%20stop%20and%20slept%20there.%20I%20later%20went%20to%20Bandra%20station%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20police%2C%20according%20to%20the%20chargesheet.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744613760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2F7uvvto9o_saif-ali-khan-attacker_625x300_22_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsaif-ali-khan-knife-attack-saif-attacker-planned-robbery-for-rs-30-000-to-get-fake-aadhaar-pan-cops-8160008%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Bangladeshi%20intruder%20who%20broke%20into%20actor%20Saif%20Ali%20Khan's%20home%20and%20stabbed%20him%20before%20escaping%20wanted%20to%20steal%20Rs%2030%2C000%20to%20get%20a%20fake%20Aadhaar%20card%20and%20a%20PAN%20card%20made%2C%20Mumbai%20Police%20have%20told%20the%20court%20in%20its%20chargesheet.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsaif-ali-khan-knife-attack-saif-attacker-planned-robbery-for-rs-30-000-to-get-fake-aadhaar-pan-cops-8160008%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Risked%20My%20Life%20To%20Expose%20Scam'%3A%20Whistleblower%20After%20Me