rth%20American%20theatrical%20release%20through%20Eastern%20Edge%20Films.%20The%20family%20drama%2C%20which%20has%20already%20claimed%20the%20title%20of%20Vietnam%E2%80%99s%20highest-grossing%20spiritual%20film%20with%20nearly%20%2410%20million%20in%20domestic%20box%20office%20receipts%2C%20will%20strategically%20debut%20during%20Asian%20American%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Naman%20Ramachandran%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2025%2Ffilm%2Fnews%2Fthe-ancestral-home-vietnam-hit-north-america-release-1236368663%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Bangladesh%20And%20The%20Art%20Of%20Instigation%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAn%20Indian%20response%20to%20the%20provocation%20by%20Bangladesh's%20Chief%20Adviser%2C%20Mohammed%20Yunus%2C%20was%20inevitable.%20While%20on%20a%20visit%20to%20China%2C%20Yunus%20had%20called%20India's%20Northeast%20'landlocked'.%20The%20remark%20by%20Yunus%20alluded%20to%20the%20perception%20of%20Bangladesh%20being%20the%20guardian%20of%20access%20to%20the%20Indian%20Northeast%20through%20the%20sea%20routes%20as%20the%20land%20route%20ran%20through%20a%20constricted%20corridor.%20Yunus%20suggested%20that%20this%20geographical%20positioning%20presents%20significant%20opportunities%20for%20China%2C%20proposing%20that%20Bangladesh%20could%20serve%20as%20an%20extension%20of%20the%20Chinese%20economy%20by%20facilitating%20production%20and%20trade%20activities%20aimed%20at%20both%20China%20and%20global%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20Let-Up%20In%20Tensions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20response%20and%20the%20actual%20interpretation%20of%20what%20Yunus%20said%20and%20meant%20are%20important%20issues%20in%20the%20emerging%20standoff%20between%20India%20and%20Bangladesh.%20Despite%20the%20one-on-one%20meeting%20at%20the%20BIMSTEC%20Summit%20in%20Bangkok%2C%20between%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Chief%20Adviser%20Mohammad%20Yunus%2C%20there%20appears%20no%20let-up%20in%20the%20rising%20tensions%20between%20the%20two%20countries.%20The%20Indian%20response%20has%20been%20to%20put%20an%20end%20to%20the%20June%202020%20initiative%2C%20under%20which%20India%20allowed%20Bangladeshi%20export%20cargo%20to%20transit%20through%20Indian%20land%20customs%20stations%20enroute%20to%20third%20countries%2C%20via%20Indian%20ports%20and%20airports.%20The%20New%20Delhi%20airport%20is%20one%20such%20important%20outlet%20for%20Bangladesh.%20This%20arrangement%20facilitated%20smoother%20trade%20flows%20for%20Bangladesh's%20exports%20to%20nations%20such%20as%20Bhutan%2C%20Nepal%2C%20and%20Myanmar%20-%20in%20particular%2C%20to%20nations%20where%20goods%20moved%20by%20land%20routes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20April%208%2C%20post%20the%20provocation%20by%20Yunus%2C%20India%20rescinded%20this%20facility%2C%20citing%20significant%20congestion%20at%20its%20airports%20and%20ports.%20This%20led%20to%20logistical%20delays%20and%20increased%20costs%20for%20Indian%20exporters.%20Internationally%2C%20this%20is%20being%20interpreted%20as%20a%20response%20to%20what%20Yunus%20said%20and%20meant.%20The%20negative%20effect%20on%20Bangladesh%20exports%2C%20especially%20after%20the%2037%25%20tariff%20also%20imposed%20by%20the%20US%2C%20will%20indeed%20be%20mind-boggling%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20uncalled-for%20and%20unnecessary%20buccaneering%20by%20Yunus%20under%20Jamaat%20pressure.%20Yunus%20and%20the%20Jamaat%20leadership%20may%20be%20unaware%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20India%20has%20a%20major%20contribution%20to%20the%20growth%20of%20the%20garment%20industry%20in%20Bangladesh%20-%20as%20much%20as%20%241.20%20billion%20worth%20of%20cotton%20yarn%20and%20raw%20cotton%20worth%20%24556.84%20million%20were%20exported%20by%20India%20to%20Bangladesh%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Possible%20Chinese%20Airfield%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20also%20studying%20reports%20of%20a%20Chinese%20plan%20to%20build%20an%20airfield%20in%20Bangladesh's%20Lalmonirhat%20district%2C%20which%20is%20sure%20to%20be%20a%20challenge%20for%20New%20Delhi's%20security%20interests%20along%20the%20eastern%20border%2C%20including%20the%20Chicken's%20Neck%20area%2C%20that%20is%2C%20the%20Siliguri%20Corridor.%20The%20area%2C%20considered%20a%20strategic%20vulnerability%20for%20India%2C%20is%20a%20sliver%20of%20territory%20that%20provides%20access%20to%20all%20transportation%20and%20energy%20arteries%20to%20Northeast%20India%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20petroleum%20pipeline%20to%20Nepal.%20Several%20power%20grids%20crisscross%20the%20narrow%20territory.%20About%2045-50%20kilometres%20to%20the%20north%20is%20the%20strategic%20Chumbi%20Valley%2C%20separating%20the%20Indian%20state%20of%20Sikkim%20and%20Bhutan%2C%20where%20the%20famous%20(though%20some%20call%20it%20infamous)%20'Trijunction'%20exists.%20Adjacent%20to%20it%20is%20Doklam%2C%20which%20every%20Indian%20by%20now%20probably%20knows%20about%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%2072-day%20long%20standoff%20between%20Indian%20and%20Chinese%20forces%20in%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20is%20this%20to%20be%20an%20airfield%20to%20be%20occupied%20by%20the%20Bangladesh%20air%20force%3F%20Or%2C%20will%20the%20Chinese%20air%20force%20place%20its%20assets%20here%20under%20a%20strategic%20partnership%20agreement%3F%20If%20assets%20are%20deployed%20here%20for%20the%20dual%20purpose%20of%20maintaining%20an%20eye%20over%20the%20Bay%20of%20Bengal%20(much%20less%20likely)%20and%20posing%20a%20threat%20to%20India's%20interests%2C%20this%20will%20surpass%20arrangements%20that%20China%20has%20with%20even%20Pakistan%2C%20in%20PoK%20and%20Gilgit-Baltistan%20areas.%20So%2C%20at%20best%2C%20this%20must%20be%20seen%20as%20good%20psychological%20warfare%20to%20hem%20India%20in.%20Lalmonirhat%20is%20just%2015%20kilometres%20from%20the%20India-Bangladesh%20border.%20It%20won't%20be%20wrong%20to%20expect%20the%20Chinese%20air%20force%20to%20display%20an%20unprofessional%20approach%20towards%20defence%20and%20strategic%20cooperation%20with%20Bangladesh%20were%20it%20to%20place%20assets%20at%20such%20an%20airfield.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Slew%20Of%20Pakistani%20Visits%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20end%20of%202024%2C%20the%20Pakistan%20army%20has%20been%20making%20a%20beeline%20for%20Bangladesh.%20In%20January%202025%2C%20a%20high-level%20ISI%20delegation%20led%20by%20Major%20General%20Shahid%20Amir%20Afsar%20had%20visited%20Dhaka%2C%20marking%20one%20of%20the%20first%20significant%20engagements%20between%20the%20ISI%20and%20Bangladeshi%20officials%20in%20decades.%20The%20agenda%20probably%20focused%20on%20military%20and%20intelligence%20cooperation%2C%20including%20discussions%20on%20establishing%20an%20intelligence-sharing%20network%20between%20the%20two%20countries.%20The%20objective%20of%20that%20step%20does%20not%20need%20a%20second%20analysis.%20For%20the%20first%20time%20since%201971%2C%20the%20Pakistan%20army%20is%20set%20to%20train%20Bangladeshi%20military%20personnel.%20Starting%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFebruary%202025%2C%20training%20sessions%20were%20to%20be%20conducted%20in%20multiple%20cantonments%20across%20Bangladesh%2C%20beginning%20with%20the%20one%20in%20Mymensingh%2C%20all%20supervised%20by%20senior%20officers%20of%20the%20Pakistan%20Army.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bangladesh%20army%20views%20itself%20as%20professional%2C%20and%20second%20to%20none.%20Its%20leadership%20seeks%20to%20showcase%20itself%20in%20various%20UN%20missions%20and%2C%20often%2C%20overreaches%20itself%20in%20projection.%20Why%20such%20a%20force%20needs%20to%20bring%20in%20Pakistani%20training%20advisers%20is%20questionable.%20Can%20they%20be%20attempts%20at%20establishing%20intelligence%20bases%3F%20As%20I%20have%20always%20said%2C%20India%20left%20Bangladesh%20after%20defeating%20and%20evicting%20the%20Pakistan%20Army%20way%20back%20in%20January%201972%2C%20but%20Pakistan%20never%20left%20Bangladesh.%20It%20always%20maintained%20a%20shadowy%20presence%20there.%20Sheikh%20Hasina's%20government%20and%20Awami%20League%20cadres%20ensured%20that%20Pakistani%20Islamism%20remained%20under%20control.%20Her%20government%20also%20resisted%20former%20Pakistan%20President%20Zia%20ul%20Haq's%20infamous%20strategy%20of%20using%20Islamism%20to%20drive%20an%20anti-India%20circle%20around%20and%20within%20India.%20Now%20with%20Hasina%20gone%20and%20the%20Awami%20League%20itself%20under%20severe%20strain%2C%20the%20potential%20to%20revive%20the%20Zia%20plan%20seems%20bigger%20than%20ever%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EDemons%20At%20Every%20Corner%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20high-level%20delegation%20from%20Pakistan's%20Foreign%20Office%20is%20scheduled%20to%20visit%20Bangladesh%20this%20month%2C%20marking%20a%20significant%20step%20in%20revitalising%20bilateral%20ties%2C%20which%20have%20remained%20largely%20dormant%20for%20over%20a%20decade.%20Ishaq%20Dar%2C%20Pakistan's%20Deputy%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20Foreign%20Minister%2C%20is%20slated%20to%20visit%20Dhaka%20on%20April%2022%20at%20the%20invitation%20of%20Bangladesh's%20Foreign%20Affairs%20Adviser%2C%20Md%20Touhid%20Hossain.%20Similarly%2C%20Pakistan%20Foreign%20Secretary%20Amna%20Baloch%20is%20scheduled%20to%20arrive%20for%20a%20Foreign%20Secretary-level%20meeting%20on%20April%2017.%20The%20visits%20can%20be%20seen%20as%20part%20of%20efforts%20to%20restore%20the%20old%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIs%20India%20seeing%20demons%20at%20every%20corner%2C%20and%20are%20Indian%20analysts%20giving%20Pakistan%20and%20Bangladesh%20more%20than%20what%20their%20strategic%20worth%20merits%3F%20These%20are%20relevant%20questions%20in%20the%20face%20of%20an%20obvious%20attempt%20by%20a%20non-strategically-inclined%20Chief%20Advisor%20to%20directly%20target%20India.%20The%20entire%20controversy%20about%20the%20'landlocked'%20nature%20of%20Northeast%20India%20was%20an%20obvious%20red%20herring.%20That%20it%20was%20made%20despite%20full%20knowledge%20of%20a%20much%20sought-after%20meeting%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20a%20week%20later%20points%20to%20deliberate%20instigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20of%20the%20Pakistan-Bangladesh%20shenanigans%20is%20yet%20to%20unfold%20even%20as%20there%20is%20a%20growing%20impatience%20in%20India%20about%20the%20intransigence%20on%20display.%20So%20far%2C%20the%20Indian%20response%20has%20invariably%20been%20measured%20and%20effective.%20This%20is%20the%20approach%20that%20usually%20wins%20strategically%20perched%20awkward%20situations.%20The%20government%20needs%20appreciation%20for%20handling%20this%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(%3Cem%3EThe%20writer%20is%20a%20Member%20of%20the%20National%20Disaster%20Management%20Authority%2C%20Chancellor%20of%20the%20Central%20University%20of%20Kashmir%2C%20and%20Former%20GOC%20of%20the%20Srinagar-based%2015%20Corps.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744609920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F8g7ufbe_yunus-xi-_625x300_28_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fbangladesh-and-the-art-of-instigation-8159599%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Is%20India%20seeing%20demons%20at%20every%20corner%2C%20and%20are%20Indian%20analysts%20giving%20Pakistan%20and%20Bangladesh%20more%20than%20what%20their%20strategic%20worth%20merits%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fbangladesh-and-the-art-of-instigation-8159599%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jaat%20struggles%20in%20North%20America%20as%20it%20mints%20only%20Rs%202.75%20crore%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744609308000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2