er%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F299507%2Feco-friendly-mud-red-stone-kerala-home-skylights-elliptical-windows-save-on-electric-bills%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ematerial%E2%80%99s%20resistance%20to%20weather%20and%20erosion%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20addition%2C%20the%20carbonation%20process%20involved%20in%20the%20solidification%20of%20the%20lime%20helps%20sequester%20carbon%20and%20reduce%20climate%20change.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EArchitects%2C%20take%20notes%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20While%20lime%20is%20versatile%20to%20work%20with%2C%20Vinoth%20says%20architects%20should%20comprehend%20its%20types%2C%20properties%2C%20and%20appropriate%20applications.%20%E2%80%9CMaterial%20sourcing%2C%20quality%20assurance%2C%20and%20the%20development%20of%20skilled%20labour%20are%20paramount.%E2%80%9D%20He%20adds%20that%20design%20considerations%20should%20prioritise%20breathability%2C%20ventilation%2C%20and%20long-term%20maintenance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E4.%20Moss%20walls%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHave%20you%20ever%20thought%20about%20moss%20as%20a%20building%20material%3F%20Architects%20Mitu%20Mathur%20and%20Shriya%20Diwan%20of%C2%A0%20GPM%20Architects%20and%20Planners%20heroed%20it%20in%20one%20of%20their%20projects%2C%20in%20line%20with%20their%20vision%20for%20a%20more%20organic%20architecture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAbout%20the%20material%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20architects%20say%20the%20material%20combines%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F352270%2Fsustainable-home-in-maharashtra-naturally-cool-summers-mango-trees-shriya-parasrampuria-prashant-dupare%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elow%20maintenance%20and%20sustainability%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20bringing%20a%20biophilic%20touch%20to%20interiors.%20The%20%E2%80%98walls%E2%80%99%2C%20they%20add%2C%20require%20no%20watering%20or%20sunlight.